---
import Features2 from '~/components/widgets/Features2.astro';
import Features3 from '~/components/widgets/Features3.astro';
import Hero from '~/components/widgets/Hero.astro';
import Stats from '~/components/widgets/Stats.astro';
import Steps2 from '~/components/widgets/Steps2.astro';
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'About us',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <!-- Hero Widget ******************* -->

  <Hero
    tagline="About us"
  >
    <Fragment slot="title">
      2007年4月発足、阪大のセクマイ団体
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="title">
      Founded in April 2007, LGBTQ+ Community at the University of Osaka.
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      割合的にはゲイ・バイの方が多いですが、<br>
      ビアン、FtM、MtF、Aセクなど様々なセクシャリティのメンバーがいます。<br>
      中には自分のセクシャリティがよくわかんないって人も。それでもいいんです！<br>
      <br>
      「同じような友達がほしい！」<br>
      「出会い系には抵抗がある...」<br>
      「いきなり夜の世界はちょっと...」<br>
      「色々な人と話してみたい！」<br>
      <br>
      こんな気持ちを持っている方、大歓迎です。<br>
    </Fragment>

    <Fragment slot="subtitle">
      Although the majority of our members identify as gay or bisexual, <br>
      we also have lesbians, FtM, MtF, asexuals, <br>
      and others with various sexualities. <br>
      Some members might not even be sure about their own sexuality yet, <br>
      and that’s perfectly OK! <br>
      <br>
      "I wanna make friends who are like me!" <br>
      "I'm not comfortable with dating apps..." <br>
      "The nightlife scene may be a bit much for me at first..." <br>
      "I’d like to talk with various people!" <br>
      <br>
      If you feel this way, you are more than welcome to join us.
    </Fragment>

  </Hero>

</Layout>
